      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_682-941",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "682-941",
      "markText": "一天清晨，格里高尔·萨姆萨从一连串不安的梦中醒来，发现自己变成了一只巨大的甲虫。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=682&rangeEnd=941"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_13123-13196",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "13123-13196",
      "markText": "这时，他的父亲从后面用力给他来了一下，这一下让他终于解脱了，他远远地飞了起来，血流如注地跌进了房内。门被父亲用手杖砰地关上了，一切终于又安静下来。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13123&rangeEnd=13196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_5_10281-10319",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10281-10319",
      "markText": "他小声喊道：“亲爱的父母，我可是一直都爱着你们的。”然后就松开手坠落下去了。",
      "totalCount": 304,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10281&rangeEnd=10319"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_38985-39078",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "38985-39078",
      "markText": "他们沉默着，不知不觉地通过眼神交流了一下，认为现在也该为她寻找一个合适的丈夫了。当电车到达目的地时，他们的女儿首先站了起来，伸展着她年轻的身体，这就像是对他们新梦想和良好愿望的一种肯定。",
      "totalCount": 286,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=38985&rangeEnd=39078"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_1633-1645",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1633-1645",
      "markText": "真想让这一切都毁灭算了！",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1633&rangeEnd=1645"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_3773-3796",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3773-3796",
      "markText": "千万别像废人一样待在床上。”格里高尔对自己说。",
      "totalCount": 264,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3773&rangeEnd=3796"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_1873-1946",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1873-1946",
      "markText": "我要是和老板来这一套，大概马上就会被炒鱿鱼。但谁知道呢，也许离职了反而更好。要不是为了我父母，我早就辞职不干了，还会到老板面前，把心里话一吐为快。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1873&rangeEnd=1946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_10_4331-4365",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4331-4365",
      "markText": "事情就是这样，当你没被工作缠身的时候，你的时间总会多得令你无所适从。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4331&rangeEnd=4365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_8_15834-16061",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "15834-16061",
      "markText": "据说，卡夫卡创作《变形记》的灵感就产生于“某天早晨无望地躺在床上，发誓收不到菲莉斯的信便决不起床的时候”。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=15834&rangeEnd=16061"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_6461-6519",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6461-6519",
      "markText": "我不得不说，我们这种公司里的员工——不管您觉得这是不幸或是福气吧——因为工作，都经常得自己克服一些身体上的轻微不适。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6461&rangeEnd=6519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_26952-27013",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "26952-27013",
      "markText": "他的睡袍毫无用处地挂在衣钩上，他却穿戴整齐地在座位上打盹儿，仿佛随时准备着回到工作状态，连在家里也在等待着上级的召唤一样。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26952&rangeEnd=27013"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_5001-5050",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5001-5050",
      "markText": "先不说门是锁着的这件事，他真的应该叫人来帮忙吗？尽管处境艰难，但一想到这儿，他还是抑制不住地笑了。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5001&rangeEnd=5050"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_6_2411-2474",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2411-2474",
      "markText": "原因也很明显，经验证明，在四十天里可以通过越来越多的广告不断激发全城市民的兴趣，之后观众的兴趣就会冷淡下来，来的人数大幅减少。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2411&rangeEnd=2474"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_38690-38777",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "38690-38777",
      "markText": "随后三个人就一起离开了公寓，他们几个月以来都没这么做了，然后坐着电车来到了城外。车厢里只有他们一家，于是他们完全沐浴在了温暖的阳光下，舒服地靠在座位上，讨论着对未来生活的展望",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=38690&rangeEnd=38777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_4564-4610",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4564-4610",
      "markText": "“在七点一刻前，我一定得起床。到那时，公司里的人估计就会来问我了，因为公司七点前就会开门。”",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4564&rangeEnd=4610"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_34674-34716",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "34674-34716",
      "markText": "如果是格里高尔，他早就该意识到人是不可能这样一直和动物生活在一起的，他就会主动离开。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=34674&rangeEnd=34716"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_7067-7110",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7067-7110",
      "markText": "我一向认为您是一个安静沉着、十分理智的人，而现在您似乎突然开始放纵各种奇思妙想的情绪。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7067&rangeEnd=7110"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_18758-18814",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "18758-18814",
      "markText": "每当他们提到赚钱的事，格里高尔的第一反应就是离开门，径自扑到门旁凉爽的沙发上，因为他又尴尬又难过，浑身燥热难堪。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=18758&rangeEnd=18814"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_8_18381-18448",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "18381-18448",
      "markText": "变形后的格里高尔被视作异类而遭到鄙视、唾弃，被追打、被隔离，最后孤独地死去，这些都不由得使读者想起几千年来犹太人的不幸遭遇和悲苦命运。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300063149&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18381&rangeEnd=18448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300063149_4_6114-6181",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6114-6181",
